咩 但一定趕到七點前到</blockquote><br />\nThz ching <br />\n要唔要買定飛先？</blockquote><br />\n可以上車入錢架"},{"pid":"b1225b7b39c68c066f3ae4e7f1df3ab5f0bf66ac","tid":373683,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T11:16:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴/絲知，如果撘4點56第一班去東京嘅jr，然後轉第一班嘅N'EX得唔得</blockquote><br />\nNex頭班車7點15分先到T2唔駛諗<br />\n乘換案內幾個方法都可以7點前到<br />\n<br />\n1. 4:56山手線 五反田-日暮里，轉6:03頭班Skyliner，6:42到 (2724yen)<br />\n2. 4:56山手線到東京站，轉5:40 KBS巴士，6:45到 (1165yen)<br />\n3. 5:07地鐵淺草線到押上，轉6:05 Skyaccess特急，6:56分到 (1369yen)<br />\n<br />\n東京站巴士再早都有班次，但記住最早既山手線都要5:13先到<br />\n<a href=\"http://honyaku.j-server.com/LUCKEISEIB/ns/tl.cgi/http://www.keiseibus.co.jp/kousoku/timetable.php?id=25&amp;SLANG=ja&amp;TLANG=zhb&amp;XMODE=0&amp;XCHARSET=utf-8&amp;XJSID=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhonyaku.j-server.com%2FLUCKEISEIB%2Fns%2Ftl.cgi%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.keiseibus.co.jp%2Fkousoku%2Ftimetable.php%3Fid%3D25%26SLANG%3Dja%26TLANG%3Dzhb%26XMODE%3D0%26XCHARSET%3Dutf-8%26XJSID%3D0&d=O6BCfiSzhlV6ZlY4K8ylW54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=db7c6eb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://honyaku.j-server.com/LUCKEISEIB/ns/tl.cgi/http://www.keiseibus.co.jp/kousoku/timetable.php?id=25&amp;SLANG=ja&amp;TLANG=zhb&amp;XMODE=0&amp;XCHARSET=utf-8&amp;XJSID=0</a>"},{"pid":"0f689fb52ce70e3dc24e20eb5bd80627d8824959","tid":373683,"uid":133959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凌晨4:29係五反田站搭山手線頭班車去日暮里搭sky access去到T2先6點3</blockquote><br />\n頭班車4:56先到五反田，5:25到日暮里，但特急5:22走，岩岩爭幾分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a87f3e0d053fd88bdd5fc02c0492c5fa591b3c","tid":373683,"uid":30150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"比我直接入機場訓算數"},{"pid":"50911e6763bce92d8a69f84c601bafc8231ddedf","tid":373683,"ui